{"tid":330010,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"各位巴絲知唔知邊度有藍牙transmitter賣？","createTime":"2017-07-20T22:33:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-20T22:33:04.000Z","uid":129593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a7a8dfe87e21b86bc284e6150a610df14033ecf0","tid":330010,"uid":129593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T22:33:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/21/061920_d308f84237a710897656db39bca2cd2c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F21%2F061920_d308f84237a710897656db39bca2cd2c.jpg&h=95521746&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.avantree.com/multipoint-bluetooth-transmitter-avantree-tc418.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.avantree.com%2Fmultipoint-bluetooth-transmitter-avantree-tc418.html&d=86y7bduWeKzVYXz27mamYxv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=ae70db28\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.avantree.com/multipoint-bluetooth-transmitter-avantree-tc418.html</a><br />\n<br />\n睇中左呢個 貪佢可以直接input optical cable駁電視<br />\n但依加仲係pre-order period 佢又冇得訂 心急想知有冇其他牌子都係可以直接插optical audio cable又差唔多價位🤔<br />\n<br />\n主要係想將藍牙耳機駁落電視機度 但又唔想買幾個transmitter optical轉3.5mm先再轉藍牙 駁上駁先駁到藍牙耳機 又煩又貴 直接插得optical就正👍🏻<br />\n<br />\n唔該晒各位巴絲"}]}